    "body": "## Problem\n\nDescribe the problem (concisely).\n\n## Steps to reproduce\n\n<img width=\"2542\" height=\"518\" alt=\"Image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/39b49fe6-005f-4edb-b1fd-e60753d86772\" />\n\n```\nnvim --clean --cmd 'se verbose=1' --cmd \"lua require('vim._core.ui2').enable{}\" --cmd 'lua vim.schedule_wrap(vim.api.nvim_input)(\":%s/.\\\\\\\\{//\")'\n```\n\n## Expected behavior\nNo spam.\n\n## System info\n\n- Nvim version (nvim -v): `v0.13.0-dev-218 ga7d65a6188-dirty` neovim/neovim@a7d65a6188\n- Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?: ?\n- Operating system/version: Linux 6.19.11-zen1-1-zen\n- Terminal name/version: kitty\n- $TERM environment variable: `xterm-kitty`\n- Installation: ?\n\n",
